# Videos Directory

This directory contains video demos and tutorials for EasyConfigs.

## Required Videos:

### Feature Demonstrations
- `configuration-demo.mp4` - Step-by-step visual configuration process
  - Should show: Plugin selection → Form filling → Real-time YAML generation → Export
  - Duration: 30-60 seconds
  - Format: MP4, optimized for web
  - Resolution: 1080p or higher

### Tutorial Videos (Future)
- `getting-started.mp4` - Complete getting started tutorial
- `mythicmobs-demo.mp4` - MythicMobs specific configuration demo
- `custom-schema.mp4` - How to add custom plugin schemas

## Video Guidelines:
- Keep file sizes under 10MB when possible
- Use MP4 format with H.264 encoding
- Include captions/subtitles when possible
- Show clear UI interactions and results
- Use consistent branding and color scheme
- Include smooth transitions and clear narration
